Author: katebishophawkguy
Text: you've come to associate it with something negative and a sense of shame and need to reverse engineer the why and where it might have started growing up

Author: BOOKWORMCat2004
Text: well, that’s all a part of the disorder, diagnosed or not. :/  everyone has different reasons, whether it be that they feel invalid if they eat, or they have such a fear of gaining weight that eating anything gives them anxiety. you’ve got to step back and look at why you feel this way.   ❤️
